1:30 restless 
i roll around unable to escape the reality of the world and slip into the mesmerizing wold of dreams i jump up in search of a stable something to help lull me out of this dreary existentce. perhaps a glass of milk and a cookie. The bright lights hurt my eyes to my dismay no milk can be found. the pantry reminds me of the cartoons where nothing is in there but cobwebs.the sound of the car starting is almost deafening at two in the morning. The blair of the music keeps me, well actually i was not sleepy so it was just good to drown out the screaching produced when singing occurs.mmm milk and a coffe doughnut nothing better in life. The sound of prrrrrrrr is alll i remember as the cat lulled me to sleep aroound 2:00

3:30 jolt

the feeling of cold sweat, an inability to breath, a cold shiver drifts across my spine, and goosbumps run across my whole body.  was it a dream or did i hear a voice

 i never have woken up like this before 

well maybe it was my computer i left it running with a cd in it berfor i went to sleep. 

no it was my uncle he called my phone around 3:45 then the home a minute later he was looking to pick up his four wheelers at 4 in the morning.
well let me start with a little history my uncle is manic depressive and has gone beyond the far end. he was kicked out of the house and soon faces a divorce but will not take his medicine to get under controle. i would not like to face him as he is.he is no longe rthe uncle i knew and loved he is dead to me. i refused to open the door for him and eventually he left. 
the one fear i have is that he had another person with hiim i did not know. i know that nobody he knew befor he went manic would be with him so it could have been some person looking to rob the home. 
this was not the beginning to a day i was hoping for.i went home knowing the only reason they did not break into the home was because i was there.
why is it a necassary rule for family to let you down. i will never trust family for anything ever again

this is no idication to the mood i may be having at the moment simply wished to leave a thought

Robert Frost
 
Nothing Gold Can Stay

Nature's first green is gold, 
Her hardest hue to hold. 
Her early leaf's a flower; 
But only so an hour. 
Then leaf subsides to leaf. 
So Eden sank to grief, 
So dawn goes down to day. 
Nothing gold can stay.

ok so life what is it really. life is a plan set out befor us the path we take the story we tell nothing more nothing less. ok so is that really it is life ust something we do something that is put in front of us a thing that gos forces upon us or is it free will is life all that people blow it up to be. what is so special about the people we meet the jobs we take the money we make.we live in this little planet scraping by to make the most of it fo maybe 80-90 years and that is it. is this a life god wants his greatest creation to face. is the purpose of this world for us to grow learn and overcome. or is this world a play pin for god. what if he put us here set us in motion then let us go like wind up monkeys. are we like entertainment in a circus. well i do not think so. i know my plan i know my path i am a servant of god and will never faulter. i will put myself on a cross t obring people to believe the world is a place god has made to teach us and allow us to gain salvation not just be handed it by being "saved". the world is gods tool to let his creation balance his free will and earn eternal life. i am not saying people must gain his love or protection because that is always eternal and never faultering. life is a game and i want to learn the rules.

Life is a novel a real page turner atleast lately new friends come in and old ones go out but to what purpose why do friends come and go. why do people have big hearts and little hearts. why do people take advantage of those willing to do all they can for someone else even if they barely know them. is this world built this way and if it is what kind creator would want it that way. i know i trust in gods plan but why do other people i mean really when it is so easy to believe in deism or even athiesm.what kind of sick creation is this where a religeon can free a man from damnation after killing another simply cause they are saved whether they are sorry for what they have done or not. what kind of world is this where the only place a person should feel fully safe is just as corrupt as the world they live in.after one reads all this reasons it all out and still believes his god is a just creator a father a protector a loving being full of all the power of this world and the next. only then does one deserve the right to tell me what my life is about and only then do they hold the true faith in god jesus and the holy spirit.the holy trinity the creator of all that is our lives. i leave this to be pondered not judged so do not leave fucking stupid questions about my faith. unless you truly want to know about it then i am open to all discussion. thank you for your time and do remember to let a flower fall. thank you.
